        <updateDate>2026-06-24T13:59:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution designates May 16, 2026, as Kids to Parks Day.</p><p>The resolution recognizes the importance of outdoor recreation and the preservation of open spaces in promoting the health and education of the young people of the United States.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
